]]></contentSummary><contentType>website</contentType><subject>curriculum</subject><webLink xml:lang="en"><![CDATA[http://studieadres.nl]]></webLink></contentLink><programDescription xml:lang="nl"><![CDATA[The programme explores the critical elements of international migration and the incorporation of immigrants in the societies they enter. It teaches students advanced theories, techniques, and methodologies in the field of Migration Studies, so that they will be able to translate perceived societal problems into relevant social scientific research questions and contribute to their solutions by combining insights from fundamental social theory with substantive theories.

This Master is unique to Europe. It brings together those who have an interest in creating a shared outlook for Europe in terms of migration studies. Partner universities not only teach but also research migration-related issues, and are so able to offer students state-of-the art knowledge in related specialisation areas.]]></programDescription><programDescription xml:lang="en"><![CDATA[The Joint European Master in International Migration and Social Cohesion (MISOCO) explores the critical elements of international migration and the incorporation of immigrants in the societies they enter. It teaches students advanced theories, techniques, and methodologies in the field of Migration Studies, so that they will be able to translate perceived societal problems into relevant social scientific research questions and contribute to their solutions by combining insights from fundamental social theory with substantive theories.

This Master is unique to Europe. It brings together those who have an interest in creating a shared outlook for Europe in terms of migration studies. Partner universities not only teach but also research migration-related issues, and are so able to offer students state-of-the art knowledge in related specialisation areas.

The students are selected on the basis of their qualifications. There is also the possibility of an Erasmus Mundus Scholarship.]]></programDescription><programName xml:lang="nl"><![CDATA[International Migration and Social Cohesion (Erasmus Mundus Master)]]></programName><programName xml:lang="en"><![CDATA[International Migration and Social Cohesion (Erasmus Mundus Masters)]]></programName><programSummary xml:lang="nl"><![CDATA[This two-year Erasmus Mundus Master's programme in International Migration and Social Cohesion (MISOCO) offers students the opportunity to study international migration in three European countries.]]></programSummary><programSummary xml:lang="en"><![CDATA[This two-year Erasmus Mundus Master's programme in International Migration and Social Cohesion (MISOCO) offers students the opportunity to study international migration in three European countries.]]></programSummary><searchword xml:lang="en"><![CDATA[migration
